channel.title: Whats wrong?!?!?!?!?!?!?!?
channel.description: What the hell is wrong with you people?! So what if Pwned deleted all the topics it gives a fresh start. I'm not complaining at all even though i lost about 30 posts. But still posting "Pwned Your Gay" aint helping? Do you think posting that will fix what already happened??? Well your wrong if you think it will you're just spamming making the situation worse! And whats up with all of the "http://mopar.google.com". Just everyone get over it. We together can rebuild the community. I know it will be hard but hell the all the tuts and downloads and almost everything got deleted. But we never did this. Did we!! No we just kept trying and trying and made everything better! Just keep in mind if you spam/flame you will be banned/muted/warned/moderated! The rules still apply. So everyone why don't we stop the spamming and build the community back up!!!!!!
